details.sectionContent: The World of GOT is here.
If you are a member of game of thrones family, then this event is yours. Show us your capabilities to win the Throne.

Participants will have to choose one chit out of which names:- ICE OR FIRE. Then there will be puzzle quiz based on time limit. Whosoever has less time will qualify and top 3 finishers will have a surprise advantage in the next round.
Decrypt the Dothraki language with the key provided by us and lead your group towards the throne to win
Hunt and scan the QR code to obtain the characters of Game of Thrones. Merge all the scraps to get the finalized picture. Group finishing with least time span wins
